{"tid":1158732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"$1600電個貨不對版既頭","createTime":"2019-05-17T07:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T06:58:10.000Z","uid":254120,"like":9,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a055a23165d00d355de91bccc7ef61e423f4a00a","tid":1158732,"uid":254120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T07:26:19.000Z","msg":"係ig見到呢個post<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MFXSeOk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMFXSeOk.png&h=a3475dc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUpk78q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUpk78q.png&h=b7ad6759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到佢整d頭都幾靚<br />\n就約左時間整<br />\n<br />\n問左價<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZtzYanN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZtzYanN.png&h=fc4fd441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我都預$1000左右電頭髮所以都ok<br />\n<br />\n之後去到我話想整呢個頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2MnfcBD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2MnfcBD.png&h=865b7682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢摸幾下個頭，就話我個頭1定要焗油<br />\n太草，唔焗唔得<br />\n我就問佢焗油幾錢，佢話$600<br />\n我就諗，如果佢電得靚既話，加埋$1600都值既<br />\n就豁出去啦<br />\n<br />\n跟住就開始剪髮、落軟髮、拉直、圈曲、定型、焗油<br />\n佢話拉直圈曲同焗油都會有個儀器係後面熱<br />\n<br />\n之後整整下都由夜晚6點半整到11點<br />\n聽到佢地話ot啊，趕收工啊咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10點左右就定型，定完就要洗頭，洗完頭仲訓左係到個人話而家直接搽埋焗油，用毛巾包住一陣就係焗油<br />\n我就即刻問焗油唔係要用儀器咩<br />\n佢就答我話其實無分別<br />\n實係佢地趕收工就hea整<br />\n<br />\n果下我就諗，我加左$600，就係用毛巾焗果幾分鐘？？<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就幫我吹番乾個頭<br />\n叫我買營養液<br />\n話我個頭唔用會好差<br />\n我都無理佢話唔要<br />\n佢就fine<br />\n<br />\n電到出黎個頭係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cU6WGyE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcU6WGyE.png&h=27b06ccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jb60oNY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJb60oNY.png&h=7aa949c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完全不對版喎<br />\n<br />\n訓醒仲要係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3yXbvtk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3yXbvtk.png&h=2ba37325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問焗完油仲會係咁草咩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Spb0oOx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSpb0oOx.png&h=7bcc8e81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2VnnB8y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2VnnB8y.png&h=b48ce9b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我就打俾佢問下有無得搞<br />\n佢話番我轉頭，話我無買營養液<br />\n用完唔會係咁<br />\n我想講整完果陣用完營養液都一樣係草啦<br />\n<br />\n$1600電把草出黎真係好嬲！"},{"pid":"3ee2c2566594f67e3dbc5a8e3004990f29dbe356","tid":1158732,"uid":128287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T07:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402672c892d9670960069ef70f8dbb4bd1a39680","tid":1158732,"uid":113922,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T07:31:13.000Z","msg":"女人錢真係易呃"},{"pid":"06848d07ab4ffcf05fea5f8f31d1d91242693469","tid":1158732,"uid":227581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T07:32:44.000Z","msg":"絲打髮質唔好 仲敢去電髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間野又on9拎條毛巾焗油根本無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6849e6cef51cf83fd8fb4b5fd9d4c9bb56e7609","tid":1158732,"uid":7343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T07:33:15.000Z","msg":"你個頭型咁大"},{"pid":"b4c9451374c3569badad2d4f831da9f6107ad199","tid":1158732,"uid":52122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6849e6cef51cf83fd8fb4b5fd9d4c9bb56e7609","tid":1158732,"uid":7343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T07:33:15.000Z","msg":"你個頭型咁大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T07:34:53.000Z","msg":"屌 我以為係一個男人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"